1)install git get url from google download it for the windows and keep 
2)then go to the terminal of your project folder and run command git init 
3)then create main branch with command "git branch -M main" (create default branch as main instead of master)
4)then create one README.md file in your project folder
5)add something to readme file as of just we kept it as namaste react

6)now lets push code to git 
 	6.1)git add . (it will push all the files)
	6.2)git commit -m "episode-01" (to commit code changes)
	6.3)so  now we need to verify the user details if first time for that follow 
	6.4)git config --global user.name "Adarsh Reddy"
	6.5)git config --global user.email "adarshreddy713@gmail.com"
	6.6)git config --global --list
	6.7)You should see:user.name=Adarsh Reddy
		      	   user.email=adarshreddy713@gmail.com
	6.8)after that git add . and git commit once again now code changes will be pushed 
	6.9)now add Add remote: git remote add origin git@github.com:mosurupodiadarshreddy/namaste_react.git
